Warning:
Subject of a SaferParty caution because the blotter contains over 150ug of LSD.

SaferParty writes: An average in 2014 of analyzed LSD blotter contained 70.4 micrograms of LSD. High doses increase risks even for experienced users. Such a high dosage can cause very intense psychedelic experience, which may be disturbing and scary. Paranoid ideation may occur. Furthermore, a so-called hypersensitivity can happen. Music, light and other stimuli can be perceived as extremely unpleasant. Even mind-body dissociation can occur.
